column5: There was a good stack of fish,so decided to play with the under water camera. It,s a bit long,but learning how to edit. So all the video is under water.  https://youtu.be/FqEGHQGEg5k
Nice Brian,no shortage of perch and blue gill I see !!
Very cool Brian..Great footage!  Were you floating around in the pontoon?
Very cool Brian..Great footage!  Were you floating around in the pontoon?  No Mike. My toon is out of commision right now. I was at the Barrie marina. There was a father and young son playing around.
Man oh man that is a lot of sunfish my kids could deep hook
That was fun to watch!  Great video Brian!
